```mermaid
graph TD
    Start --> |(Farmer) Create Profile| Blockchain
    Blockchain --> |Store Farmer's Profile| System
    System --> |Assign Unique ID| Blockchain
    Blockchain --> |Record Profile Creation| End

    Start --> |(Farmer) Submit Application| Blockchain
    Blockchain --> |Record Application Submission| System
    System --> |Automatically Assign Field Officer| Blockchain
    Blockchain --> |Record Verification| System
    System --> |Schedule Regular Checkups| Field Officer

    Field Officer --> |Regular Checkup| Blockchain
    Blockchain --> |Record Checkup Details| System
    System --> |Send Notification to Farmer| End

    Blockchain --> |Issue Certificate| Farmer
    Farmer --> |View Certificate| End
